   <talk_paragraph index="n799_academin_npc-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n799_academin_npc-1-a" mid="13" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Tell about what I talked with Jasmine)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Investigator of the Past${sound:npc_LM_2nd_Academic_sp_05.ogg}<BR>So you believe me now?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n799_academin_npc-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n799_academin_npc-1-b" mid="15" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(.........)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Investigator of the Past$<BR>Yes, it's all true. Our jewel has been losing its energies. If the energy totally runs out, we'll be dull and finally wait for death.<BR>The worst thing is... we'll be alive for a long time while our body's dead.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n799_academin_npc-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n799_academin_npc-1-c" mid="17" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Is there a way...?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Investigator of the Past$<BR>
There is a way to prevent running out our jewel's energy... will you try?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n799_academin_npc-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n799_academin_npc-1-d" mid="19" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Investigator of the Past${action:Talk}<BR>I was also just like you. My jewel was running out of the energy and I thought that I was going to die.<BR>At that moment, someone who was in the same situation told me the way....<BR><FONT color=#7e12d3>(The investigator adjusts her glasses)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n799_academin_npc-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n799_academin_npc-1-e" mid="21" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>How can I find another jewel? I haven't seen other investigators....</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Investigator of the Past$<BR>The reason why the jewel is running out of energy is because it is unstable now.<BR>
The jewel isn't able to control the power inside of it and the power is leaking out through cracks. To solve this problem, you should absorb another empty jewel to expand the size of your jewel.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n799_academin_npc-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n799_academin_npc-1-f" mid="23" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Investigator of the Past$<BR>You and I are the only ones who're still alive.<BR>The one who told me this method was <FONT color=#a82424>DX-08</FONT> and she died too.<BR>Her jewel had lost too many energies, so it wasn't impossible to recharge it. However, you're still okay. You have about ten days left.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n799_academin_npc-1-f" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="300503" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n799_academin_npc-1-g" mid="25" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Why are you telling me this?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Investigator of the Past$<BR>I'll tell you where the jewel is.<BR>
If you go to <FONT color=#a82424>West Ancient armoury</FONT>, you will be able to find <FONT color=#a82424>XD-22's jewel</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n799_academin_npc-1-g" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="300498" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Investigator of the Past$<BR>
